data.description: In the heart of Eagle Mountain, you will find this gorgeous gem!  Why buy new construction when you can have this home? Just a little over a year old, but fencing, landscaping, patio, and RV pad are all done for you. With such an elegant feel and upgrades you will simply fall in love with this home.  Don't wait--Come see it today!  There is room to grow....basement is about 45% finished.  The 3rd garage is tall and deep enough for RV storage.     All info is provided as a courtesy estimate only including Square footage figures (were obtained from tax record and previous MLS listing) .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement and confirm all info.
